title: Hunter the Age of Magic (complete JPEGs)
description:
The complete Vertigo series Hunter: the Age of Magic (issues 1-25), plus prequel miniseries The Names of Magic (1-5), as JPEGs. No ads! :-)

If you want the entire Books of Magic saga, there are some other good torrents around with the whole thing, starting with the Neil Gaiman-John Bolton miniseries; this torrent just has the Dylan Horrocks-Richard Case run.

Enjoy!
